title: Kodiak Golf

creator: Kodiak Codeworks
descriptionHtml:
Kodiak Golf ease-of-use makes it the perfect app for the everyday player. Built to make golf more fun, Kodiak Golf is designed for quick entry of scores, fun side games, and stat tracking.

Stats: Find strengths and opportunities to improve. With Kodiak Golf Stat Tracker, statistics are made easy. Tracking 15 statistics you’ll improve your game just by knowing which area to focus on. Fairway percentage, greens in regulation, fairway to green in regulation, par 3 green in regulation, putts per hole, 1-putt percentage, 3-putt percentage, par 3 average, par 4 average, par 5 average, scrambling percentage, birdie conversion, birdy to bogey ratio, fairway to par percentage, fairway to birdie percentage.

Full Round History: Review old rounds and track scoring history, free, in one safe location. Helps to improve your game.

Social: Follow friends and be notified of their rounds on the turn and finish. Share your rounds with sharing tools.

Side Games: Bragging rights on the line? Play one of many side games: Skins, Nassau, Stableford, Wolf, Sixes, Las Vegas, Low Ball-High Ball. Kodiak Golf Ledger will track all the action and tabulate results for easy viewing at the end of the round.

Tournament Management: From weekend parties to club championships. Organize a large group into a tournament is now made fun. We’ve simplified the admin of large groups and tournament play. Collecting scorecards and compiling results made easy with Kodiak Golf.

TV Support: View the tournament on any TV in the clubhouse. Updated in real-time, leaderboards are broadcast to the app and TV in the clubhouse. Golfers can commiserate or celebrate over the leaderboard while making the turn, or waiting for the other golfers to finish up.

Tournament sponsor? Display tournament sponsors in-app while golfers are scoring their rounds.

Tournament communications: Send notifications in-app to all players. Shot-gun starts? Weather issues? Send a notification.
descriptionShort: Live Scoring and Leaderboard for Your Tournament

Kodiak Golf ease-of-use makes it the perfect app for the everyday player. Built to make golf more fun, Kodiak Golf is designed for quick entry of scores, fun side games, and stat tracking.

Stats: Find strengths and opportunities to improve. With Kodiak Golf Stat Tracker, statistics are made easy. Tracking 15 statistics you’ll improve your game just by knowing which area to focus on. Fairway percentage, greens in regulation, fairway to green in regulation, par 3 green in regulation, putts per hole, 1-putt percentage, 3-putt percentage, par 3 average, par 4 average, par 5 average, scrambling percentage, birdie conversion, birdy to bogey ratio, fairway to par percentage, fairway to birdie percentage.

Full Round History: Review old rounds and track scoring history, free, in one safe location. Helps to improve your game.

Social: Follow friends and be notified of their rounds on the turn and finish. Share your rounds with sharing tools.

Side Games: Bragging rights on the line? Play one of many side games: Skins, Nassau, Stableford, Wolf, Sixes, Las Vegas, Low Ball-High Ball. Kodiak Golf Ledger will track all the action and tabulate results for easy viewing at the end of the round.

GPS Distances: Over 10,000 courses with Hole and Tee locations. Distances are displayed on a Map view with front, middle and back green yardages.

Tournament Management: From weekend parties to club championships. Organize a large group into a tournament is now made fun. We’ve simplified the admin of large groups and tournament play. Collecting scorecards and compiling results made easy with Kodiak Golf.

TV Support: View the tournament on any TV in the clubhouse. Updated in real-time, leaderboards are broadcast to the app and TV in the clubhouse. Golfers can commiserate or celebrate over the leaderboard while making the turn, or waiting for the other golfers to finish up.

Tournament sponsor: Display tournament sponsors in-app while golfers are scoring their rounds.

Tournament communications: Send notifications in-app to all players. Shot-gun starts? Weather issues? Send a notification.

Wear OS: Initial watch support added to view yards

descriptionHtml:
Kodiak Golf ease-of-use makes it the perfect app for the everyday player. Built to make golf more fun, Kodiak Golf is designed for quick entry of scores, fun side games, and stat tracking.

Stats: Find strengths and opportunities to improve. With Kodiak Golf Stat Tracker, statistics are made easy. Tracking 15 statistics you’ll improve your game just by knowing which area to focus on. Fairway percentage, greens in regulation, fairway to green in regulation, par 3 green in regulation, putts per hole, 1-putt percentage, 3-putt percentage, par 3 average, par 4 average, par 5 average, scrambling percentage, birdie conversion, birdy to bogey ratio, fairway to par percentage, fairway to birdie percentage.

Full Round History: Review old rounds and track scoring history, free, in one safe location. Helps to improve your game.

Social: Follow friends and be notified of their rounds on the turn and finish. Share your rounds with sharing tools.

Side Games: Bragging rights on the line? Play one of many side games: Skins, Nassau, Stableford, Wolf, Sixes, Las Vegas, Low Ball-High Ball. Kodiak Golf Ledger will track all the action and tabulate results for easy viewing at the end of the round.

GPS Distances: Over 10,000 courses with Hole and Tee locations. Distances are displayed on a Map view with front, middle and back green yardages.

Tournament Management: From weekend parties to club championships. Organize a large group into a tournament is now made fun. We’ve simplified the admin of large groups and tournament play. Collecting scorecards and compiling results made easy with Kodiak Golf.

TV Support: View the tournament on any TV in the clubhouse. Updated in real-time, leaderboards are broadcast to the app and TV in the clubhouse. Golfers can commiserate or celebrate over the leaderboard while making the turn, or waiting for the other golfers to finish up.

Tournament sponsor: Display tournament sponsors in-app while golfers are scoring their rounds.

Tournament communications: Send notifications in-app to all players. Shot-gun starts? Weather issues? Send a notification.

Wear OS: Use your watch to view yardages. Also, you can enter Shot Tracking data. To view the yardages, just make sure to open the Round once on your phone. For Shot Tracking, make sure to open Shot Tracking at least once on the phone.
descriptionShort: Live Scoring and Tournament Leaderboard | Golf Score Tracker, GPS & Maps
